; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/230
; Description: Omitting currency from cost should not break lot matching
; Expected: No errors - cost currency should be inferred

2000-01-01 open Assets:Abc ABC
2000-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances USD
2000-01-01 open Expenses:Abc USD

2026-01-02 * "Sale"
  Assets:Abc                                              -1 ABC {1 USD}
  Expenses:Abc

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance"
  Assets:Abc                                               1 ABC {1}
  Equity:Opening-Balances -1 USD
